data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!! BUYER FINANCING fell through. This Home is Ready for a Quick Move-In.  There is Lots of Space in this Well-Maintained 5 Bedroom/3 Bath Home.  There's a Guest Bedroom and Full Bath on the Main Floor.  Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring throughout the downstairs.  You'll find Granite Counters, Stainless Steel Appliances, Tile Backsplash and Pantry in the Kitchen. Upstairs you'll find a Super-Sized Primary Bedroom with vaulted ceiling and En Suite Bathroom with 2 sinks, Shower with Glass Door, Separate Tub, Water Closet and Extra Large Clothes Closet.  The other 3 Bedrooms and Full Hallway Bathroom are also Upstairs, along with the Laundry Room, that includes a Washer and Dryer.  The Flat Backyard, with NO NEIGHBORS BEHIND, is fully Fenced.  Front and Back yards have a 2-zone sprinkler system.  Walk to the Neighborhood Pool.  CLOSE TO FORT EISENHOWER, Schools and Shopping.  House is Clean and Move-In Ready.  100% FINANCING AVAILABLE for Qualified Buyers through Local Lender. Call for details.
